{"tid":583485,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【九巴解僱風波】林鄭：九巴有改善空間　指政府樂做調停角色","createTime":"2018-03-07T04:43:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-07T04:45:06.000Z","uid":39464,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"484d01c8243712aff8c20e081762b58d12858a13","tid":583485,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T04:43:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180307/s00001/f36ea709e8e1ce303e6ac625ca18826c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180307%2Fs00001%2Ff36ea709e8e1ce303e6ac625ca18826c.jpg&h=1b659640&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n九巴昨解僱「九巴月薪車長大聯盟」成員4名車長，雙方會面後九巴宣布暫緩解僱。行政長官林鄭月娥中午表示，良好勞資關係是社會和諧重要一環，強調政府重視勞資關係，會竭盡所能介入及調停。<br />\n<br />\n她表示，未完全了解情況，不過初步認為九巴在處理上有改善空間。至於有意見要求政府介入，她說政府樂意擔當調停角色，目前勞工處已接觸勞資雙方跟進。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180307/s00001/1520397478807\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180307%2Fs00001%2F1520397478807&d=Td7eeswRvvpBVkGphoyX%2BQHZiNw4JStbf0cW9gpNrZc%3D&h=1da35a64\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180307%2Fs00001%2F1520397478807&h=8a3c9fb5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180307/s00001/1520397478807</a>"},{"pid":"38a259e3576b53538c6c6ffc3b030197f17dcc0a","tid":583485,"uid":102096,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T04:44:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d4b5d12eda6ec5cafdd39ca0d6dcd53ad6dbe4a4","tid":583485,"uid":81052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T04:44:41.000Z","msg":"獨立調查委員會呢?"},{"pid":"47e62ea2075c74731e695bbbf22ab2ab18fb29d1","tid":583485,"uid":49208,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T04:45:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload